title: Parrot Finance to Begin PRT Token Buyback on Monday, Capping Fiery Vote
description: Solana-based protocol Parrot Finance will buy PRT tokens from all sellers at $0.0045 apiece.

title: CFTC Overreached in Suing Binance, Crypto Exchange Says
description: The U.S. Commodity Futures Trading Commission (CFTC) is reaching beyond its jurisdiction in trying to sue Binance, the global crypto exchange said in a motion to dismiss the regulator's lawsuit against it.
